{"tid":657362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真定假？傳費Sir甦醒兼開口說話","createTime":"2018-05-08T04:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T07:44:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb7a9fd5c9cd592a60ebe6ee63fb53911aa6d57","tid":657362,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Qp6g70ogGxeTF%2Bo8yHqdFzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c505b253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】費Sir醒番喇？有傳費格遜在手術後已經從昏迷中醒過來，而能坐起來說話。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》周一爆料，根據費格遜（Sir Alex Ferguson）好友指，這名正在沙福特皇家醫院留醫的曼聯傳奇領隊，於上周六入院做緊急腦出血手術，在昏迷多天後終於甦醒，而且可以坐起來說話。<br />\n<br />\n這名好友表示：「預期的費Sir康復情況良好，他在足球界最親密的好友一同把事情的最新狀況保密。」不過，費Sir醒過來這傳聞，仍未被並家人及曼聯證實。<br />\n<br />\n76歲的費格遜在出事後，獲多方祝福，紅魔中場卡域克表示：「我在上周六下午收到消息，真的不敢相信，之後立即向數名球會中人詢查費Sir的情況。我很關心他，他是我的前主帥及朋友，對我十分重要。」"},{"pid":"afbe921e8bc816d258c9a5817c89597f10ed2cb1","tid":657362,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"費Sir頂住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18c3746a447c794f3c054ca7787889fa0be45ad","tid":657362,"uid":4496,"like":12,"dislike":41,"score":-29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"迴光反照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c01399443dc406aee9350904435a5cf41d10787","tid":657362,"uid":4168,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"希望老費早日康復"},{"pid":"ac9c2d3376d957a6e889b3e97ac866d85e0fe931","tid":657362,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":12,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c18c3746a447c794f3c054ca7787889fa0be45ad","tid":657362,"uid":4496,"like":12,"dislike":41,"score":-29,"citedBy":3,"re